channel.title: I can only get on my server no one else can why?
channel.description:
OK, well i just started making this server i have asked two people, too try can get on my server both of them can't get on they say it says "Error connecting to server" I'm like wtf, why can I only get on? If you can tell me how to fix this error i have in my server i would be very happy. It is a Jordiescape V2. So if your familiar with this type of server source, and error please post. I really need to know.
Please and thank-you ~Badho56~
